1218.name: E NiCrMo 686 CPT
1218.Applications: E 686 CPT electrode for welding duplex, super-duplex and super-austenitic stainless steels as well as nickel alloys such as UNS N06059 and N06022, Inconel alloy C-276 and Inconel alloys 622, 625 and 686.
1218.Suitable_For: Joining Duplex, Superduplex, super austenitic stainless steel, nickel alloys, N06059, N06022, Hastelloy C276, alloy C22, Inconel 622, 625, 686, chemical and petrochemical industry, 2.4605, 2.4610, 2.4602, 2.4819, NICr23Mo16Al, NiMo16Cr15Ti, NiCr21Mo14W, NiMo16Cr15W, alloy 59, alloy C4, alloy 276
